[[TITLE]] The Operating Manual
[[TAGS]] aster os operating system table contents
[[DESCRIPTION]] The table of contents and overview of the AsterOS Manual.

AsterOS is a non-POSIX operating system, and so many of its internals will
mystify the average *nix user on first boot. This manual seeks to bridge that
gap somewhat by providing detailed and technical overviews of the various
operating system functionalities and capabilities.
